------ So, in order to select the title of all the songs from the 'Pop' artists, I first have to created a query that lists all artists from the first
table that are in the pop genre. Then I use the IN operator to select the titles of the songs where the arist is listed on my previous quesried results. 

SELECT name 
FROM artists
WHERE genre="Pop";

SELECT title FROM Songs WHERE artist IN (SELECT name FROM artists WHERE genre="Pop");


